mmarquee.automation.uiautomation

Interface IUIAutomation

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.sun.jna.platform.win32.COM.IUnknown
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IUIAutomation2, IUIAutomation3, IUIAutomation4, IUIAutomation5

    public interface IUIAutomation
extends com.sun.jna.platform.win32.COM.IUnknown
    Wrapper for the IUIAutomation COM interface. Exposes methods that enable UI Automation client applications to discover, access, and filter UI Automation elements. UI Automation exposes every element of the UI Automation as an object represented by the IUIAutomation interface. The members of this interface are not specific to a particular element.
    Author:
    Mark Humphreys Date 06/07/2016.
